{
  "texts": [
    "The procedure text and structured JSON are combined using a prompt template (see Supporting Information) modified from Stanford Alpaca.",
    "46 A sequence length limit of 2048 tokens based on LLaMA tokenizer, is imposed due to memory considerations in fine-tuning the language models.",
    "This sequence limit reduces the number of records to 1,300,613 (97.11%) of 1,339,260.",
    "The cumulative distribution function of sequence lengths is shown in Figure S1.",
    "A subset of 100K records, hereinafter referred to as USPTO-ORD-100K, is randomly selected from the 1,300,613 records."
  ]
}